N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 463.8 - Reporting

State Regulations
(a) The provision
of social, educational, or medical services shall be reported to the Social

Services Information System (SSIS) under Item 30, Services: Code 16, Family-Planning Services. (b) The
social services official shall report to the department periodically, as
required, data from the documentation required to be maintained in agency
records. Notes
